{
	"ID": "20221112155318-cawoyml",
	"Type": "NodeDocument",
	"Properties": {
		"id": "20221112155318-cawoyml",
		"title": "000 OpenShift基础概念",
		"updated": "20221112161539"
	},
	"Children": [
		{
			"ID": "20221112155420-ppxj7f5",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 1,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155420-ppxj7f5",
				"updated": "20221112155453"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "1. Operator"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112155435-cl59pht",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 2,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155435-cl59pht",
				"updated": "20221112161521"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "1.1  什么是 Operator"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112155526-41jirfl",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155526-41jirfl",
				"updated": "20221112160426"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\tOperator 是 RedHat 收购的 CoreOS 公司最早发起的一项有助于 Kubernetes 运维的技术框架体系。它可以将一套复杂系统环境（例如：主备或 HA 数据库、包含多个微服务+数据库的应用环境）所涉及到的所有资源、配置、最佳实践整体打包，并基于 CRD 提供对相关资源提供针对性运维管理操作（创建、备份、恢复、自愈等），从而帮助 Kubernetes 运维管理员简化对这些系统的运维操作、降低运维难度。\n \tOpenShift 提供并运行了大量的 Operator。根据重要程度，我们可以将这些 Operator 分为“"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeMark",
					"Data": "mark",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeMark2OpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "集群 Operator ”和“常规 Operator”"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeMark2CloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "两类。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112155634-euvstv0",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 2,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155634-euvstv0",
				"updated": "20221112155702"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "1.2 集群Operator"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112155703-7wzowxa",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155703-7wzowxa",
				"updated": "20221112160235"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\tOpenShift 底层依赖的系统级服务都是以 Opertor 的方式运行的，例如 DNS、 Etcd。这些服务不是直接运行在 OpenShift 依赖的 Linux 操作系统上，而是以 ClusterOpertor (co) 的方式运行在 OpenShift 中，在"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeMark",
					"Data": "mark",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeMark2OpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "安装 OpenShift 的阶段就会将 ClusterOpertor"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeMark2CloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 安装好。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112155730-1edxtnq",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112155730-1edxtnq",
				"updated": "20221112160300"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\t在 OpenShift 控制台的 “集群设置” 中查看集群中所包含的 “集群 Operator” 环境。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112160307-wivki5w",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112160307-wivki5w",
				"updated": "20221112160309"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "\t"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "image.png"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/image-20221112160309-9r7tgfn.png"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112160303-yz7d5li",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112160303-yz7d5li",
				"updated": "20221112160329"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "查看 OpenShift 中包含的所有集群 Operator"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112160331-26oi032",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20221112160331-26oi032",
				"updated": "20221112160331"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeCodeSpan",
					"Data": "code",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanContent",
							"Data": "$ oc get clusteroperator "
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20221112160351-2osjxos",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
